bathtubs come ashore but no cocaine yet if he does he said hed 
leave the package on the beach and call police 
nine times out of 10 they might think it was mine to begin 
with he said 
the cocaine thats been discovered will be flown to dallas where 
federal authorities will destroy it caldwell said 
its pretty potent he said i imagine there have been some 
people sick who see this on television but some of it might still 
be in the gulf 
