elephant in 10 years 
hundreds of government officials diplomats journalists and 
conservationists watched tuesday as moi put a torch to the 12 tons 
ivory atop a 20foot pile of wood 
the pyre was placed on a hill in nairobi national park 
overlooking the vast athi plains that are home to gazelle rhino 
giraffe zebra lions and other wild animals 
actions speak louder than words moi said kenya cannot 
appeal to the world to stop buying ivory if at the same time we are 
