disagrees with a bush administration proposal to lift restrictions 
on exporting personal computers to soviet bloc nations 
i do not support that decision cheney told reporters 
my concern is that it will give them a computer capability that 
has military applications that should be avoided the secretary 
said 
it gives them significant capabilities they do not now 
possess he said 
cheney termed inaccurate a washington post report that he had 
